Package: PopHivePlots
Title: PopHIVE Brand Styling for ggplot2 Visualizations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person(given = "Shoa", family = "Moosavi",
         email = "shoa.moosavi@yale.edu",
         role = c("aut","cre")),
  person(given = "Yiren", family = "Hou",
         email = "yiren.hou@yale.edu",
         role = c("aut"))
	)
Description: Provides standardized ggplot2 themes and color palettes consistent 
    with PopHIVE branding. Simplifies the creation of publication-ready 
    visualizations including choropleth maps, line graphs, dot plots, and bar charts
    with a single main function that applies appropriate styling automatically.
